workDescription1: As a Software Developer specializing in frontend technologies, I collaborate with cross-functional teams to design and implement user-friendly interfaces. Utilizing my expertise in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, I develop responsive and visually appealing web applications. Additionally, I integrate third-party APIs, optimized code for various browsers.
workDescription2: In my role as a Full Stack Software Developer, I engage in end-to-end software development, covering both frontend and backend components. Leveraging technologies such as Node.js, Express, and MongoDB on the server side, and Vue.js on the client side, I create scalable and maintainable applications. I design and implement RESTful APIs, manage databases, and ensure data security. I contribute to the development lifecycle, from concept to deployment, and actively participated in code reviews to maintain high coding standards.
